## A simple circuit model for scaling effects in timing

### purpose and importance of the research
Timing ranks among the most fundamental computations of the brain. 
Evidence suggests the brain encodes time through controlling the speed of neural state evolution (Meirhaeghe et al. 2021, Wang et al. 2018)

